          <h1>Diet Taken by Good Body</h1>
          <div class="container">
            <p>This is a sample HTML page that shows some examples of diet taken by good body. A good body is not only achieved by exercise, but also by eating healthy and balanced food. Here are some of the foods that can help you build a good body.</p>
            <div class="diet">
              <div class="diet-item">
                <img src="/waffles-2190961_1280.jpg" alt="Eggs">
                <h3>Eggs</h3>
                <p>Eggs are a great source of protein, which is essential for muscle growth and repair. Eggs also contain healthy fats, vitamins, and minerals that can boost your energy and metabolism. You can eat eggs for breakfast, lunch, or dinner, and prepare them in different ways, such as boiled, scrambled, or poached.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="diet-item">
                <img src="chicken-3212144_1280.jpg" alt="Chicken">
                <h3>Chicken</h3>
                <p>Chicken is another high-protein food that can help you build a good body. Chicken is lean and low in calories, which can help you lose fat and gain muscle. Chicken also contains iron, zinc, and selenium, which are important for your immune system and overall health. You can eat chicken grilled, baked, or roasted, and add some spices and herbs for flavor.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="diet-item">
                <img src="salmon-1238248_1280.jpg" alt="Salmon">
                <h3>Salmon</h3>
                <p>Salmon is a fatty fish that is rich in omega-3 fatty acids, which are good for your heart, brain, and joints. Omega-3 fatty acids can also reduce inflammation and improve blood flow, which can help you recover faster from your workouts. Salmon also provides protein, vitamin D, and B vitamins, which can support your muscle growth and energy levels. You can eat salmon baked, grilled, or smoked, and pair it with some vegetables and grains.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
